    • DatabaseAccess

      public DatabaseAccess(User user, AccessType accessType, ObjAccessed objManipulated, int objID)
      DatabaseAccess constructor that also adds the object immediately to the accessList.
      Parameters:
      user - The user that preformed the Database Access.
      accessType - The type of access performed.
      objManipulated - The object affected (Customer or Appointment).
      objID - The unique int identifier of the object affected.
